England Wins Toss, Will Bowl First in Third India Cricket Test

-- B y   B o b   B e n s c h
-- 
2011-08-10T09:39:05Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-08-10/england-wins-toss-will-bowl-first-in-third-india-cricket-test.html
England  won the toss and will bowl
first in the third cricket Test match against  India  at Edgbaston
in Birmingham.  England has won the first two games in the four-Test series
and can replace India as No. 1 in the International Cricket
Council rankings with another victory or by drawing the final
two matches.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Bob Bensch at 
 bbensch@bloomberg.net  